00:41.473 --> 00:44.810
(Cheryl) OH, THERE'S
MY LITTLE SOCCER STAR.

00:44.844 --> 00:48.146
GRACIE, TELL US WHY WE SHOULD
PAY FOR ANOTHER YEAR OF SOCCER.

00:48.179 --> 00:51.317
I'M OUT OF YOUR HAIR
FOR THREE HOURS EVERY SATURDAY.

00:51.350 --> 00:53.518
YOU MAY CONTINUE.

00:53.551 --> 00:55.755
HERE'S A CHECK.

00:55.787 --> 00:57.089
NEXT!

00:57.122 --> 01:00.759
OH, GOD.
A TAP-DANCING CHILD?

01:00.792 --> 01:03.630
BETTER EARN THOSE
FANCY SHOES OF YOURS, GIRL.

01:25.284 --> 01:27.387
SIGN IT.

